parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission clutch can cause the vehicle to jerk, shudder, or stall, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or shudders when shifting gears
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or fails to accelerate
the check engine warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCM can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission fails to shift properly
the vehicle stalls or fails to accelerate
the check engine warning light is illuminated
error messages are displayed on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission actuator can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission fails to shift properly
the vehicle stalls or fails to accelerate
the check engine warning light is illuminated
error messages are displayed on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Mount and Transmission Mount Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine mount and transmission mount can cause the vehicle to vibrate excessively, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates excessively
the engine mount and transmission mount are worn or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the evap purge system can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or fails to start
the evap purge system is faulty or malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock up or become difficult to turn, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes stiff or locks up
a warning message appears on the dashboard
grinding or rubbing noises when turning
loss of power steering assist
difficulty steering
and jerky or sticky steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering rack can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn or lock up, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Grinding or rubbing noises when turning
difficulty steering
jerky or sticky steering
and loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electric power steering module can cause the power steering system to fail, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Loss of power steering assist
difficulty steering
and a warning message appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission problems can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or lose power while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving
jerks or lurches forward
has difficulty shifting gears
loses power
or has a delayed response to acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The clutch problems can cause the vehicle to jerk, stall, or lose power while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle jerks or lurches forward
or the vehicle has difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel system problems can cause the vehicle to stall, shut off, or lose power while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving
shuts off
or loses power
the fuel gauge fluctuates
or the vehicle has difficulty starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system problems can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's systems malfunction
such as the sound system
backup assist
or clock
or the vehicle's battery drains quickly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The door latch problems can cause the door to not shut properly, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The door latch does not function properly
or the door does not shut.
